 when the believing women come to you as emigrants, examine them. Allah is most knowing as to their faith. And if you know them to be believers, then do not return them to the disbelievers; they are not lawful [wives] for them, nor are they lawful [husbands] for them. But give the disbelievers what they have spent. And there is no blame upon you if you marry them when you have given them their due compensation. And hold not to marriage bonds with disbelieving women, but ask for what you have spent and let them ask for what they have spent. That is the judgement of Allah; He judges between you. And Allah is Knowing and Wise."}},"11":{"w":[{"b":"0.15","h":"0.75","c":"وَإِن","d":"wa-in","e":"And if","i":"وَاِنۡ"},{"b":"1.3","h":"1.85","c":"فَاتَكُمۡ","d":"fātakum","e":"have gone from you","i":"فَاتَكُمۡ"},{"b":"2.3","h":"3.29","c":"شَيۡءٞ","d":"shayon","e":"any","i":"شَىۡءٌ"},{"b":"3.8","h":"5.08","c":"مِّنۡ","d":"min","e":"of","i":"مِّنۡ"},{"b":"4.1","h":"5.47","c":"أَزۡوَٰجِكُمۡ","d":"azwājikum","e":"your wives","i":"اَزۡوَاجِكُمۡ"},{"b":"5.4","h":"7.23","c":"إِلَى","d":"ilā","e":"to","i":"اِلَى"},{"b":"5.8","h":"7.71","c":"ٱلۡكُفَّارِ","d":"l-kufāri","e":"the disbelievers","i":"الۡكُفَّارِ"},{"b":"6.9","h":"9.27","c":"فَعَاقَبۡتُمۡ","d":"faʿāqabtum","e":"then your turn comes","i":"فَعَاقَبۡتُمۡ"},{"b":"8.3","h":"11.17","c":"فَـَٔاتُواْ","d":"faātū","e":"then give","i":"فَاٰ تُوا"},{"b":"9.1","h":"12.3","c":"ٱلَّذِينَ","d":"alladhīna","e":"(to) those who","i":"الَّذِيۡنَ"},{"b":"10.0","h":"13.49","c":"ذَهَبَتۡ","d":"dhahabat","e":"have gone","i":"ذَهَبَتۡ"},{"b":"10.8","h":"14.62","c":"أَزۡوَٰجُهُم","d":"azwājuhum","e":"their wives","i":"اَزۡوَاجُهُمۡ"},{"b":"13.0","h":"16.93","c":"مِّثۡلَ","d":"mith'la","e":"(the) like","i":"مِّثۡلَ"},{"b":"13.4","h":"17.69","c":"مَآ","d":"mā","e":"(of) what","i":"مَاۤ"},{"b":"15.1","h":"19.11","c":"أَنفَقُواْۚ","d":"anfaqū","e":"they had spent","i":"اَنۡفَقُوۡا​ ؕ"},{"b":"17.2","h":"24.1","c":"وَٱتَّقُواْ","d":"wa-ittaqū","e":"And