:"Most Merciful","i":"رَّحِيۡمٌ"}],"a":{"g":"O Prophet, when the believing women come to you pledging to you that they will not associate anything with Allah, nor will they steal, nor will they commit unlawful sexual intercourse, nor will they kill their children, nor will they bring forth a slander they have invented between their arms and legs, nor will they disobey you in what is right - then accept their pledge and ask forgiveness for them of Allah. Indeed, Allah is Forgiving and Merciful."}},"13":{"w":[{"b":"0.12","h":"0.36","c":"يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا","d":"yāayyuhā","e":"O you","i":"يٰۤاَيُّهَا"},{"b":"2.7","h":"2.88","c":"ٱلَّذِينَ","d":"alladhīna","e":"who","i":"الَّذِيۡنَ"},{"b":"3.7","h":"4.2","c":"ءَامَنُواْ","d":"āmanū","e":"believe","i":"اٰمَنُوۡا"},{"b":"4.7","h":"5.68","c":"لَا","d":"lā","e":"(Do) not","i":"لَا"},{"b":"5.1","h":"6.19","c":"تَتَوَلَّوۡاْ","d":"tatawallaw","e":"make allies","i":"تَتَوَلَّوۡا"},{"b":"6.3","h":"7.9","c":"قَوۡمًا","d":"qawman","e":"(of) a people","i":"قَوۡمًا"},{"b":"7.1","h":"8.86","c":"غَضِبَ","d":"ghaḍiba","e":"(The) wrath","i":"غَضِبَ"},{"b":"7.8","h":"9.93","c":"ٱللَّهُ","d":"l-lahu","e":"(of) Allah","i":"اللّٰهُ"},{"b":"8.6","h":"11.04","c":"عَلَيۡهِمۡ","d":"ʿalayhim","e":"(is) upon them","i":"عَلَيۡهِمۡ"},{"b":"9.5","h":"12.48","c":"قَدۡ","d":"qad","e":"Indeed","i":"قَدۡ"},{"b":"9.8","h":"12.89","c":"يَئِسُواْ","d":"ya-isū","e":"they despair","i":"يَــٮِٕـسُوۡا"},{"b":"10.8","h":"14.23","c":"مِنَ","d":"mina","e":"of","i":"مِنَ"},{"b":"11.","h":"14.65","c":"ٱلۡأٓخِرَةِ","d":"l-ākhirati","e":"the Hereafter","i":"الۡاٰخِرَةِ"},{"b":"15.7","h":"16.42","c":"كَمَا","d":"kamā","e":"as","i":"كَمَا"},{"b":"16.3","h":"17.37","c":"يَئِسَ","d":"ya-isa","e":"despair","i":"يَــٮِٕـسَ"},{"b":"17.2","h":"18.26","c":"ٱلۡكُفَّارُ","d":"l-kufāru","e":"the disbelievers","i":"الۡكُفَّارُ"},{"b":"18.4","h":"20.15","c":"مِنۡ","d":"min","e":"of","i":"مِنۡ"},{"b":"18.8","h":"20.7","c":"أَصۡحَٰبِ","d":"aṣḥābi","e":"(the) companions","i":"اَصۡحٰبِ"},{"b":"19.9","h":"22.26","c":"ٱلۡقُبُورِ","d":"l-qubūri","e":"(of) the graves","i":"الۡقُبُوۡرِ"}],"a":{"g":"O you who have believed, do not make allies of a people with whom Allah has become angry. They have despaired of [reward in] the Hereafter just as the disbelievers have despaired of [meeting] the inhabitants of the graves."}}}